For example, I almost didn‚Äôt to get my formal diagnosis because I‚Äôm a professional singer. That‚Äôs right; autistic people are quite capable of being entertainers. It wasn‚Äôt an easy career for me, and I had to make certain accommodations, but our medical professionals should already know that, not dismiss it.
The truth is that you can be empathetic (even highly so) AND autistic. You can be extroverted and autistic. You can be outgoing and autistic. You can be a people person and autistic. Of course, some autistics are introverted as well, but as the saying goes, ‚ÄúIf you‚Äôve met one autistic person, then you‚Äôve met one autistic person.‚Äù Ascribing generalizations to a diverse group of people only serves to harm our community.
